Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.01,0:00:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.68,0:00:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.22,0:00:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.33,0:00:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.54,0:00:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.34,0:00:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.62,0:01:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.06,0:01:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.73,0:01:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.07,0:01:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.35,0:01:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務，明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.33,0:01:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛做了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.23,0:01:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.90,0:01:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向那束花發誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.54,0:01:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終有一日迎戰的日子\N一定會來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.94,0:01:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十二話\N[迷惘的戰士們]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.28,0:02:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…推倒地球圈統一聯合的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.35,0:02:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進一步為了消滅聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.56,0:02:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續挑起戰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於聯合的組織已滲透各國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.59,0:02:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以相信會有更多人犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.83,0:02:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.67,0:02:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!我馬上叫特洛瓦來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.61,0:02:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是別勉強比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.38,0:02:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!你的朋友醒了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.32,0:02:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肚子餓了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去煮點湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.16,0:02:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巡迴表演途中的馬戲團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.16,0:02:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的藏身之所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.87,0:02:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你早已死了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.91,0:02:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗我們OZ的反對勢力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.37,0:03:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不但沒有遵從武裝解除的勸告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.78,0:03:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且在各地挑起無謂的戰火…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那次之後一個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ沒有對付衛星的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.99,0:03:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們只是鎮壓地球的軍事國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.99,0:03:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已過了一個月嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.49,0:03:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對OZ來說，你已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.47,0:03:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星對你已經沒有束縛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.14,0:03:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不可以那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.50,0:03:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被發現了嗎?\N沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.14,0:03:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那次以來，沒有新任務了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我下不了決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若OZ再用衛星作擋箭牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.85,0:03:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼辦才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.52,0:03:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者我應該向你學習嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.39,0:03:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我有一個忠告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣可會痛得要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.54,0:04:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦竟然放聲大笑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是第一次吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.37,0:04:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來到地球後\N我第一次拜託別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我失去知覺期間\N世界上發生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以告訴我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是強而有力的振翅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.58,0:04:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快上來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉!快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家出來了呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.83,0:05:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莎莉，爆破成功\N現在撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.94,0:05:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟甚麼事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是游擊隊，賓度上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追擊隊出發!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.71,0:05:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次要消滅他們!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在位於舊中國山岳地帶\N的自治區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推動和平主義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.39,0:05:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政治領導人被暗殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.92,0:05:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當全國還在哀悼時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和武裝勢力持有不同主張的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.73,0:05:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為聯合駐守部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍事政變的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.53,0:05:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主謀的賓度上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否定以往的和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.34,0:05:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他主張為了國家獨立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擴張軍備才是須要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.44,0:05:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ把聯合解體了的現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多獨立國家像這裡一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在發生內戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做甚麼?莎莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.79,0:06:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.23,0:06:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.46,0:06:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳很久沒回來故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.67,0:06:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一回來就要妳冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，是我自己的決定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.54,0:06:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家!沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事!非常成功!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.75,0:06:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.78,0:06:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陸戰用機動戰士里歐!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.23,0:06:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是賓度上校的命令\N一個不留!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.07,0:06:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.37,0:06:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了!他們去了那邊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種武器對機動戰士無效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能破壞所有監察器就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下武器投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.22,0:07:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則格殺勿論!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過無用吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,援軍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.73,0:07:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…鋼彈!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.73,0:07:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無心戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快滾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別怕!消滅他!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別看小哪吒!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.99,0:07:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.53,0:07:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈為何會在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弱者不要戰鬥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.91,0:08:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.65,0:08:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何要戰鬥?\N對著贏不了的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.81,0:08:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為非戰不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.22,0:08:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受人命令嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.42,0:08:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是!我們自願戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很累呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.57,0:08:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去我們那裡休息嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.53,0:08:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他至少不是我們的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.81,0:08:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.31,0:08:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒弄錯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.58,0:08:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有，現在傳送影像資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來沒弄錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連OZ也覺得棘手的鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨晚睡得好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用幫我運送糧食啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要報恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說到報恩，你對我們才有恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.97,0:09:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救了你們的不是我，是哪吒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪吒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.81,0:09:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部鋼彈的名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是最後一箱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟敢胡說八道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.56,0:09:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我求你!請你停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想幾位兵大哥付款…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜誰所賜你們能安心做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們拼命保護國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.44,0:09:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟然向我們收錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們說你們保護甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們只是在巴結賓度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.72,0:09:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,踐踏這個國家的和平啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.76,0:09:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭婆娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.50,0:10:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我告訴妳反抗軍隊有何下場?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.75,0:10:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是甚麼人!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.79,0:10:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!我會記著你們!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你，五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又救了我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.77,0:10:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為弱者為何要戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.64,0:10:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無資格戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.17,0:10:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.18,0:10:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不明白你為何是懦夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.28,0:10:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敗給比自己強的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是個只能和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比自己弱的對手戰鬥的懦夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你就放棄嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.66,0:11:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是為了衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.19,0:11:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了得到和平戰鬥到現在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.19,0:11:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無資格操縱哪吒戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.23,0:11:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你昨日救了我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.63,0:11:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你們是弱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.74,0:11:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，我們是弱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們不會放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.74,0:11:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是弱者才應該要增加同伴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.28,0:11:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.31,0:11:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無資格操縱哪吒戰鬥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據以上的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.80,0:11:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一帶相信是游擊隊的根據地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.47,0:11:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然終於抓到他們的尾巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但想不到鋼彈會在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.27,0:11:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的戰鬥力很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.74,0:11:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正面衝突的話\N我軍也會傷亡慘重吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候，借OZ的兵力如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向他們提議組成聯軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.35,0:12:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.92,0:12:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那會給予OZ介入本國的藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自主權怎辦!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不親自作戰，我們就對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨立國家的國民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.93,0:12:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校你說那不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拿基少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.30,0:12:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想失去你們\N這班優秀的官兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝上校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.24,0:12:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，在宣佈獨立時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經有心理準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯!上校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祖國應該由我們親手保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是獨立國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.28,0:12:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!我很清楚大家的決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.25,0:12:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就全軍出擊\N消滅游擊隊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.45,0:12:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了我們的祖國!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉，辛苦妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.77,0:12:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，那小孩不是和妳一起嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.47,0:12:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，留下那東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他去不了哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.48,0:13:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不會和我們一起戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.18,0:13:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，無人能強迫他戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.19,0:13:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他很混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.59,0:13:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為在戰爭中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.76,0:13:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他對自己有期望卻不能回應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他認為自己失去資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳那樣說一定沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為妳是聯合的軍醫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.84,0:13:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是政府軍!政府軍的攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應戰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先攻的直升機來電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現數台對機動戰士的飛彈發射器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一齊發射火前後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.53,0:13:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士部隊開始前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別理會敵人的掩護砲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集中攻擊鎮壓的機動戰士!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直升機部隊!鋼彈怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去確認!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.83,0:14:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.89,0:14:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拿基少校!發現鋼彈了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，鋼彈沒有反擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.54,0:14:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳送影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷彩網?駕駛員還未上去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.17,0:14:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賓度上校，鋼彈沒有反擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.71,0:14:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原因不明，這樣我們能取勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.15,0:14:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎，本隊也馬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.85,0:14:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來終於穩操勝卷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.92,0:14:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我來說是，對你們來說也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士部隊現在起俘虜鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.43,0:15:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以防萬一\N砲擊隊瞄準鋼彈候命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走呀…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.34,0:15:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.17,0:15:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是砲擊隊，有敵襲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是OZ的艾亞利玆!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.55,0:15:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賓度上校!OZ攻擊我軍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我軍?拉拿基
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.72,0:15:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ才是我軍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.02,0:15:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了從鋼彈手中\N保衛我們的祖國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.19,0:15:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ派來支援部隊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，反對那提議的部份軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.97,0:15:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經投靠了游擊隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校!你說甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概就是那樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的統治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.61,0:15:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會為這國家帶來和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國民應該也會理解啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.88,0:15:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國民不會希望由OZ來統治!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ說會承認本國的自主權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.75,0:16:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是由我來掌握政權呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.32,0:16:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直以來辛苦你了，拉拿基
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.23,0:16:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賓度上校!你只顧自己嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.73,0:16:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!賓度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.54,0:16:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然把這國家出賣給OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.84,0:16:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,微不足道的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重覆著無價值的戰鬥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!差一發就能擊倒它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!振作!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是弱者所以會沒命啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是強者…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.84,0:16:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅OZ…拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.38,0:17:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.02,0:17:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.49,0:17:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛，快走，這裡已經不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.86,0:17:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一會的話我們可以支持下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.22,0:17:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.89,0:17:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說甚麼!莎莉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!小子!\N你為何不戰鬥啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…沒有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別胡說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有那種力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.24,0:17:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.64,0:17:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伏低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧…?小子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.74,0:17:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了保護大家啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.51,0:17:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這種…世界裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭玩弄人類的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.76,0:17:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，不抓緊信念不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉!妳做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.90,0:17:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛\N你是個能拯球救弱者的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.47,0:17:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要失去你善良的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.94,0:18:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉\N妳為何要做那種傻事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.82,0:18:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為現在治療你的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.05,0:18:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我的生命更重要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.05,0:18:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的心的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.36,0:18:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走!莎莉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.97,0:18:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪吒!我沒資格操縱你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.67,0:18:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在\N把你的力量…借給我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.51,0:18:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來差不多消滅他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.64,0:18:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只差俘虜那部鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.95,0:18:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校!鋼彈動了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.64,0:19:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一瞬間毀了5部艾亞利玆!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.95,0:19:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.78,0:19:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我方只剩下數部艾亞利玆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他們掩護我們撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.39,0:19:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.54,0:19:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.18,0:19:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使賓度死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ也會統治這國家呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們打算繼續戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.89,0:19:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這詞語被濫用了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.76,0:20:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合和OZ也在高呼正義與和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我有我的正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.86,0:20:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家有各自的正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也應該有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.40,0:20:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.74,0:20:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正義的人一定要是強者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.68,0:20:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弱者沒資格使用哪吒的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.08,0:20:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心態錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.35,0:20:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心比以前堅強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.22,0:20:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有心的話力量有須要嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.69,0:20:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能和哪吒並肩作戰時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你再來幫我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.56,0:20:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為弱者，妳還要戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.40,0:20:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為，我的心堅強啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.24,0:20:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!大家集合!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.17,0:20:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次的公演決定了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們聽到會嚇一跳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們去OZ的基地勞軍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.98,0:20:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ基地!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.88,0:20:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我也想準備新的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.18,0:21:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要精彩刺激，軍人又歡迎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.69,0:21:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,團長，可以交給我去辦嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有甚麼主意嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.49,0:21:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有軍人一定歡迎的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦平時沉默寡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他這樣說一定沒問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.03,0:21:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，好吧，交給你啊，特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我留下糧食和車鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.51,0:21:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這裡待傷勢痊癒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.98,0:21:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有何打算?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用鋼彈作戰不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.75,0:21:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星的整體意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.65,0:21:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是部份感情偏激的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用鋼彈開始了攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.76,0:21:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中也包括我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要抗拒隨感情行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是那樣學習的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.66,0:21:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以給OZ藉口攻擊衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的理性那樣判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.94,0:21:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後就和你一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.94,0:21:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵照感情行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.94,0:21:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是你的表演裝置嗎?\N特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.01,0:21:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，請你期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.81,0:22:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會聽到熱烈的喝采聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.32,0:22:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.48,0:22:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要當是最後一次踏上舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我畢生難忘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.43,0:22:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，那是我最後的大舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.56,0:22:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.71,0:22:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.71,0:22:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.71,0:22:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.71,0:22:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.21,0:22:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.71,0:23:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.21,0:23:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.71,0:23:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.71,0:23:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.14,0:23:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以士兵為主力的OZ裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.24,0:23:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有能冷靜判斷戰爭的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.74,0:23:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,投入的戰鬥力因輕浮而失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.25,0:23:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們重覆著無意義的屠殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.18,0:23:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，OZ開始進攻宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.79,0:23:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦為了保護衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.55,0:23:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作出最後一戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.76,0:23:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年輕人急於求死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.39,0:23:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱薩琳擋在其面前!
